long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An UNOFFICIAL extension for developers using braid-design-system to quickly look up components. 

Braid is a new styling library created by SEEK but is open source. 
Check out the documentation here! https://seek-oss.github.io/braid-design-system/

This chrome extension shows a little pop up that allows you to quickly search the list of components and click it to visit the documentation.
